{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "11", "m": "11", "Y": "2025"}, "time": {"H": "04", "M": "14", "S": "41"}}, "news": [{"title": "Odisha REAT fines developer for unfair trade practices, denying possession to buyer", "para": "Odisha Real Estate Appellate Tribunal fined a developer Rs 10 lakh, comparing their \"dubious\" tactics to Shakespeare's Shylock. Despite full payment for a commercial unit, the buyer faced denied possession and demands for extra money. The tribunal ordered possession, interest, and barred further demands, emphasizing the right to shelter.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/rera/odisha-tribunal-imposes-rs-10-lakh-fine-on-developer-for-unfair-trade-practices/125239565?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-16220/125239565.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "rera"}, {"title": "Germany\u2019s Bernhard Schulte buys six floors of office space in Mumbai", "para": "Global maritime major Bernhard Schulte Shipmanagement has acquired office space in Mumbai for over Rs 304 crore. This marks a significant acquisition by an international shipping group in India. The new office will serve as the company's India headquarters. It will consolidate ship-management, crewing, technical, and digital operations. The space is scheduled for completion by December 2027.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/bernhard-schulte-expands-operations-in-india-with-major-office-acquisition-in-mumbai/125239537?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-67572/125239537.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Sirca Paints' profit grows 36% in Q2 FY26", "para": "Sirca Paints India has extended its affiliation with Sirca SPA, Italy, ensuring the esteemed brand name will be in use until 2041. The company marked a robust performance in the latest quarter, experiencing a 24% year-on-year increase in revenue to reach Rs 131 crore. Furthermore, net profit surged 36% to Rs 18 crore.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/paints/sirca-paints-profit-grows-36-in-q2-fy26/125239475?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-14142/125239475.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "paints"}]}